+## 3. 阶段一：启动注册 — Shiro 如何挂载到 Spring Boot
+
+### 3.1 FilterConfig — 将 Shiro 注册到 Servlet 容器
+
+```java
+// modules/security/config/FilterConfig.java
+
+@Configuration
+public class FilterConfig {
+
+    @Bean
+    public FilterRegistrationBean<DelegatingFilterProxy> shiroFilterRegistration() {
+        FilterRegistrationBean<DelegatingFilterProxy> registration = new FilterRegistrationBean<>();
+        registration.setFilter(new DelegatingFilterProxy("shiroFilter"));
+        registration.addInitParameter("targetFilterLifecycle", "true");
+        registration.setEnabled(true);
+        registration.setOrder(Integer.MAX_VALUE - 1);
+        registration.addUrlPatterns("/*");
+        return registration;
+    }
+}
+```
+
+**关键点：**
+- `DelegatingFilterProxy("shiroFilter")` — 将名为 `shiroFilter` 的 Spring Bean 代理为 Servlet Filter
+- `addUrlPatterns("/*")` — 拦截所有请求
+- `setOrder(Integer.MAX_VALUE - 1)` — 优先级低于 XssFilter，请求先过 XSS 清洗再过 Shiro
+
+**请求执行顺序：**
+```
+Tomcat 接收请求 → XssFilter(XSS清洗) → ShiroFilter(安全认证) → Controller
+```
+
+### 3.2 ShiroConfig — 创建 SecurityManager 与过滤器路由规则
+
+```java
+// modules/security/config/ShiroConfig.java
+
+@Configuration
+public class ShiroConfig {
+
+    // ① 会话管理器
+    @Bean
+    public DefaultWebSessionManager sessionManager() {
+        DefaultWebSessionManager sessionManager = new DefaultWebSessionManager();
+        sessionManager.setSessionValidationSchedulerEnabled(false);  // 关闭定期验证（用Token不用Session）
+        sessionManager.setSessionIdUrlRewritingEnabled(false);       // 关闭URL重写
+        return sessionManager;
+    }
+
+    // ② 安全管理器（Shiro的核心）
+    @Bean("securityManager")
+    public SecurityManager securityManager(Oauth2Realm oAuth2Realm, SessionManager sessionManager) {
+        DefaultWebSecurityManager securityManager = new DefaultWebSecurityManager();
+        securityManager.setRealm(oAuth2Realm);            // 挂载 Oauth2Realm（认证+授权逻辑）
+        securityManager.setSessionManager(sessionManager);
+        securityManager.setRememberMeManager(null);        // 不使用"记住我"
+        return securityManager;
+    }
+
+    // ③ 过滤器工厂（路由规则）
+    @Bean("shiroFilter")
+    public ShiroFilterFactoryBean shirFilter(SecurityManager securityManager,
+                                              SysParamsService sysParamsService) {
+        ShiroFilterFactoryBean shiroFilter = new ShiroFilterFactoryBean();
+        shiroFilter.setSecurityManager(securityManager);
+
+        // 注册自定义过滤器
+        Map<String, Filter> filters = new HashMap<>();
+        filters.put("oauth2", new Oauth2Filter());
+        filters.put("server", new ServerSecretFilter(sysParamsService));
+        shiroFilter.setFilters(filters);
+
+        // URL → 过滤器映射规则（LinkedHashMap，顺序匹配）
+        Map<String, String> filterMap = new LinkedHashMap<>();
+        // ... 具体规则见下节 ...
+        shiroFilter.setFilterChainDefinitionMap(filterMap);
+        return shiroFilter;
+    }
+
+    // ④ 启用 Shiro 注解支持（@RequiresPermissions 等）
+    @Bean
+    public AuthorizationAttributeSourceAdvisor authorizationAttributeSourceAdvisor(
+            SecurityManager securityManager) {
+        AuthorizationAttributeSourceAdvisor advisor = new AuthorizationAttributeSourceAdvisor();
+        advisor.setSecurityManager(securityManager);
+        return advisor;
+    }
+}
+```
+
+### 3.3 URL 过滤器路由规则
+
+使用 `LinkedHashMap`，**顺序匹配，先匹配先生效**，`/**` 作为兜底：
+
+```java
+Map<String, String> filterMap = new LinkedHashMap<>();
+
+// ─── anon 区（匿名访问，无需任何认证）───
+filterMap.put("/ota/**", "anon");                       // OTA 上报
+filterMap.put("/otaMag/download/**", "anon");            // 固件下载
+filterMap.put("/webjars/**", "anon");                    // 静态资源
+filterMap.put("/druid/**", "anon");                      // Druid 监控
+filterMap.put("/v3/api-docs/**", "anon");                // OpenAPI 文档
+filterMap.put("/doc.html", "anon");                      // Knife4j 文档页
+filterMap.put("/favicon.ico", "anon");                   // 图标
+filterMap.put("/user/captcha", "anon");                  // 获取验证码
+filterMap.put("/user/smsVerification", "anon");          // 短信验证码
+filterMap.put("/user/login", "anon");                    // 登录
+filterMap.put("/user/pub-config", "anon");               // 公共配置
+filterMap.put("/user/register", "anon");                 // 注册
+filterMap.put("/user/retrieve-password", "anon");        // 找回密码
+
+// ─── server 区（服务间通信，Bearer = server.secret）───
+filterMap.put("/config/**", "server");                   // 配置下发
+filterMap.put("/agent/chat-history/report", "server");   // 聊天上报
+filterMap.put("/agent/chat-summary/**", "server");       // 聊天摘要
+filterMap.put("/agent/chat-title/**", "server");         // 聊天标题
+
+// ─── anon 区（继续补充）───
+filterMap.put("/agent/chat-history/download/**", "anon"); // 聊天记录下载
+filterMap.put("/agent/play/**", "anon");                  // 音频播放
+filterMap.put("/voiceClone/play/**", "anon");             // 克隆音播放
+
+// ─── oauth2 区（兜底，所有未匹配的走用户Token认证）───
+filterMap.put("/**", "oauth2");
+```
+
+**决策树：**
+```
+请求 URL
+  │
+  ├── /ota/** ─────────────→ anon   → 直接放行
+  ├── /user/login ─────────→ anon   → 直接放行
+  ├── /config/** ──────────→ server → 校验 server.secret
+  ├── /agent/chat-**/report → server → 校验 server.secret
+  └── /** (其他所有) ──────→ oauth2 → 校验用户 Token
+```
